13:08.960 --> 13:11.840
and sports stars, about their mental attitude

13:11.840 --> 13:14.520
and people who've been through traumatic events about resilience

13:14.520 --> 13:17.200
and all sorts of things of that nature.

13:17.200 --> 13:21.400
I don't want to necessarily be raising things that keep getting ignored.

13:21.400 --> 13:24.600
But if the mainstream media will refuse to talk about certain things,

13:24.600 --> 13:26.360
well, someone needs to say something.

13:26.360 --> 13:29.040
And that's the only reason I've ever got into any of this.

13:29.040 --> 13:34.000
So for me, that's a sad state of...

